CIP1 has a Bruck oil cooler for $70:

http://www2.cip1.com/ProductDetails.asp?ProductCode=VWC%2D021%2D117%2D021%2DB

Although I think their distributors are no good, this oil cooler worked great. You have to modify it to fit the T4 bracket (it would appear that its from another VW/Audi vehicle and repackaged):

http://homepage.mac.com/ratwell/.Pictures/MoreParts8/49-OilCooler.jpg
http://homepage.mac.com/ratwell/.Pictures/MoreParts8/50-OilCoolerFace.jpg
http://homepage.mac.com/ratwell/.Pictures/MoreParts8/51-OilCoolerShape.jpg

Before installation:

1. remove the foam
2. file the tabs in these areas:

http://homepage.mac.com/ratwell/.Pictures/MoreParts8/52-OilCoolerFlaws.jpg

